name: Incite & Infiltrate
description:
**Full screen and headphones for 100% experience"

Welcome, commander, your mission begins now. After two decades of searching and filtering in the Milky Way Galaxy, our scouting department has narrowed our SCI(Secret Colonial Invasion) target down to the third planet surrounding the star S9237(Sun). Local civilization(Homo sapien) call their planet “Earth”. A group of elite spy force is at your disposal for the infiltration of Earth and its Homo sapiens. Prepare for Hyperjump travel immediately.
